videos.headline: UCF's INT sets up short TD run
videos.description: UConn QB Jack Zergiotis' pass is picked off by UCF's Antwan Collier. Three plays later Greg McCrae punches it in from one yard out.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCF's INT sets up short TD run) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: UCF's Davis off to the races for 73-yard TD
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel fires a pass to Gabriel Davis, who breaks a tackle and goes to the house for a 73-yard UCF score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCF's Davis off to the races for 73-yard TD) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: UCF expands lead on pick-6
videos.description: UConn's Steven Krajewski's pass is intercepted by UCF's Nevelle Clarke, who goes 48 yards for the touchdown.
